import React from 'react';
import { Box, Typography, Grid } from '@mui/material';
import QuestionButton from './QuestionButton';
import getQuestion from '../services/quizService';


const Question = ({questionText, answerText}) => {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Typography variant="h4">{questionText}</Typography>
            <Grid container spacing={2}>
  <Grid item xs={8}>
    <Item>xs=8</Item>
  </Grid>
  <Grid item xs={4}>
    <Item>xs=4</Item>
  </Grid>
  <Grid item xs={4}>
    <Item>xs=4</Item>
  </Grid>
  <Grid item xs={8}>
    <Item>xs=8</Item>
  </Grid>
</Grid>
            <Typography variant="h6">What is the capital of France?</Typography>
            <QuestionButton text={"Test"}/>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default Question
